FBIS3-11048 "drlat052_g_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-052 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Mar 1994 CENTRAL AMERICA Guatemala World Bank Official Affirms Loan Disbursement PA1503140194 PA1503140194 Article Type:BFN [Editorial Report] Guatemala City SIGLO VEINTIUNO in Spanish on 10 March, page 6, reports that, on 9 March, Claudio Sapelli, World Bank official on a two-week visit to Guatemala, affirmed that the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development will make its third loan disbursement during the second half of 1994. Guatemala has already received $48 million of the $120-million loan for the Economic Modernization program.
